channel.title: HybridScape Connecting
channel.description:
Using hybriscape svn and beta zipped are the same, client connects, then disconnects in a split second and is then stuck logged on. [code] [H] Starting HybridScape Server on 0.0.0.0:43594 [H] ClientHandler: Accepted from localhost:3772 [H] ClientHandler: Client admin disconnected. [/code] No error in console when compiling, except for usual -Xlint:depreciation message.
Any ideas?
